            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". This is why we’re not seeing a ton of 800-horsepower C8 Corvettes all over the place. Yes, this is the brave new world of automotive tuning, where you need to learn ",
